profile:
Customer satisfaction is one of our top priorities as New Look Windows & Doors. Our products are creative, top notch and always manufactured, assembled and set up by experienced workers. Top quality replacement vinyl windows, energy saving insulated steel doors, aluminum windows and vinyl patio doors, entrance doors, storm doors and porch enclosures are only a few of the products we offer, at a fair and competitive price range.

****

Did you know vinyl windows are currently the most popular types of windows all over Canada? This is only because they’re immune to rust, corrosion and almost every type of physical damage (chipping, peeling), which could only mean they’re built to last. The investment will pay off in your energy bill savings, as vinyl windows provide perfect insulation, preventing heat loss. Just to prove you we’re very confident about the quality of our products, every New Look window and door comes with a lifetime warranty that’s also transferable!
New Look windows are equipped with Energy Advantage Low E Glass, which consists of sealed glass chambers filled with inert gas (we use Argon) for more efficient thermal insulation. That way, you could save up to 30% (or even more) of your energy bills a year! New Look windows & Doors will turn your home into an exotic retreat from the frightful winter weather, and will keep the chilly air conditioning breeze inside during hot summer afternoons

profile:
BETTER INSTALLATION. LOWER ENERGY COSTS:
 
Windows and doors are one of the most significant purchases you'll make when building or renovating your home. It's something you want to get right - the first time. That's why homeowners across the GTA choose Casa Bella Windows & Doors, with more than 60 years experience in manufacturing and installation.
 
At Casa Bella, your window and door specialists:
 
•	Choose from an extensive selection of windows. From the economical Classic range to the premium Uniqwood series, we can meet your individual requirements. 
•	Our standard and specialty selection of windows include Casement Windows that are easy to operate and energy efficient; Vertical/Horizontal Sliding Windows that offers an economical design with maximum ventilation; dramatic Bay and Bow windows that make a statement, add contour and increase the natural lighting in your home; and contemporary specialty shaped that add a distinctive touch to your home. 
•	When it comes to doors, Casa Bella has a complete list of options for your home. Steel entry doors are energy efficient and can reduce your energy bills; fiberglass and wood doors add a cosy, homely touch; patio and garden doors add an extra touch of summer and allow easy access to the outdoors. 
 
At Casa Bella, we manufacture and install the best quality windows and doors. 
 
Customer service is our number one priority. We never outsource the installation of your new windows and doors to a sub-contractor. All of our professional installation crews are bonded and insured Casa Bella employees who are paid to do the job right, the first time.
 
Trust. Quality. Service
Experience the Casa Bella Advantage
For a windows and door professional you can trust…call CasaBella. 416-650-1033

profile:
WELDA Windows and Doors where Quality Doesn`t Cost - It Pays! ----WELDA Windows and Doors - Ontario’s Home Improvement Company installs Energy Star vinyl windows, residential entry doors and patio / porch / entrance enclosures to fit any home in Toronto, GTA, Ontario. If you`re planing to upgrade your windows, doors or porch enclosure and price, quality, and service are important - you need to contact WELDA Windows and Doors.--- www. weldawindows.com --- www.ontariowindowsanddoors.ca--- We also supply and install window coverings and retractable awnings. 

Please visit www.weldashading.com---

***

Whether your preference is for basic sliding windows and steel entry doors or your taste is more for casement windows and fiberglass doors,  WELDA Windows & Doors home improvement company has the solution for you.  Replacement vinyl windows in Toronto; front entrance doors in Toronto, GTA, Barrie; energy star windows in Toronto, Brampton; porch enclosures in Oakville, Oshawa;  sliding patio doors in Kitchener, Burlington, Ajax.


***

WELDA Windows and Doors offers a full line of vinyl replacement windows, residential entry doors, porch enclosures and window coverings to enhance the architectural style of any home in the Greater Toronto Area.

***

Investing in new windows and doors should be a one-time investment, so we make every effort to provide our customers with the education and understanding they need to make an informed buying decision.

***

At WELDA Windows, our approach is different. First of all, rather than "sell" you anything, we help you "buy" windows and doors by listening to your needs and then matching those needs with the right product and installation to meet those needs. Homeowners who make "informed buying decisions" based upon having all their needs met and understanding what they are purchasing are the most satisfied customers.

***

Our consultants are very skilled at walking you through the buying process, listening to your needs and concerns, explaining the features and benefits of each product and installation and arriving at the best choice to fill your needs. They can even explain the many financing options that are available to help you get the products you want, when you want them. After choices are made, our consultants can explain the installation process. Our custom installation methods and techniques assure a neat, clean, efficient installation in your home. WELDA stands behind its work like no other home improvement company. 

***

Our products & services include:
*Energy Efficient Windows & Doors, CSA Rated, Energy Star
*Single & Double Slider Window
*Awning Window
*Single & Double Hung Window
*Casement Window
*Picture Window
*Bay Windows
*Bow Windows
*Steel Entrance Door
*Fiberglass Entry Door
*Garden Hinged Door
*Exterior Sliding Patio Door
*Windows & Doors Installation
*Porch Enclosures
*Window Coverings
*Custom Interior Shutters

***

See full details of all our products on our website: www.weldawindows.com and www.ontariowindowsanddoors.ca

profile:
Whether your project is commercial or residential, new construction or renovation, replacement or historical preservation, look no further than Panorama Windows & Doors. You want a refreshing design and comfortable functionality of your windows and doors – you are at the right place. Over the years we provide and install high-quality windows and doors to our commercial and residential clients in Calgary, Medicine Hat, Lethbridge, Edmonton & surrounding areas. 
You want to instantly add value, style and security to your property that will make you the pride and envy of your neighbourhood. We offer top-quality windows and doors at very competitive prices.  Our large selection of colours and textures will exceed your expectations, our windows and doors that are made with premium materials for durability, strength, energy efficiency and security. Replacement and installation of windows and doors is done fast, with care and precision. Our experts in in installation and replacement of windows and doors provide top quality and hassle free experience with one-on-one personalized support that will exceed your expectations.

We have solutions to improve the overall impression of your home or business for your own satisfaction or to help you sell the property. From planning to installation, we don’t compromise on standards and quality of our premium windows and doors. Panorama Windows & Doors is the leader in product innovation with unmatched design flexibility, customization options in size and style, energy efficiency, and outstanding thermal, sound, safety and weather performance. 

All our services of replacement and installation of windows and doors can be done at a convenient time that will meet your time frame, and that will not interfere with your schedule. To learn more we invite you to explore our site and don’t wait, contact us today for personalized service or to request a free estimate!

profile:
Clera Windows + Doors by FM Industries has been manufacturing and installing windows and doors throughout all of Ontario since 1978.  They add beauty and value to nearly 1000 homes every month and can easily service the entire province via one of their 37 sales and installation offices.

 

Clera Windows + Doors has been recognized as one of Canada’s Best 50 Privately Managed Companies and the City of Vaughan’s Company of the Year.  Clera was recently awarded the Houzz service award for 2014 and is a proud recipient of the Homestars Best Award for 2012 and 2013. Add to these achievements a stellar A+ Better Business Bureau rating and you’ll understand why Clera Windows + Doors is the best choice for new windows and doors for your home.

 

We manufacture.  We install.  You save.

profile:
Home Decor Window & Door Centre (HDWD) is Ontario’s leading manufacturer of fiberglass entry doors. Our high quality custom door systems are made locally in Canada. 
We openly provide all relevant information about our fiberglass doors to help our customers make the right choices. We take great pride in our work. 25+ years of experience has enabled our craftsmanship to evolve to new heights. We keep innovating and improving our processes.
Our door system is superior and stronger than wood or steel and plays an important part in securing your entrance. We provide a turnkey solution – we design, build and install your front door. All done by our team of experts. We take care of the entire project.

profile:
EuroStar Windows specializes European Tilt & Turn Windows and Doors as well as North American Casement and Sliding Windows. We also offer a wide variety of European & domestic door products for the residential renovation market. 
With Showrooms in Toronto, Ottawa and Burlington, EuroStar strives to offer products at a reasonable price with the quality and performance that will impress our customers. EuroStar is very proud of our reputation in the window and door industry. The quality of our products and excellent customer service is our number one priority as we strive for continuous improvement. 
Choose EuroStar and you will not be disappointed!

profile:
Milano Windows & Doors offers high quality vinyl windows, entry doors including steel and fiberglass doors, patio doors, storm doors and porch enclosures. In addition to enhancing the look and value of your home, our Energy Star products will ensure significant savings on your energy bills.

Our master installers will exemplify professionalism and treat your home as their own. In addition, the owners of Milano Windows & Doors will personally stand behind every project by thoroughly inspecting each job once completed, to make sure our customers are 100% satisfied.

At Milano Windows & Doors, we guarantee the BEST SERVICE, the BEST PRODUCT and the BEST PRICE!

profile:
Family owned and operated A & J Windows & Doors has served Toronto and surrounding communities for over 30 years, offering sales and installation of quality doors and windows for residential and commercial customers.
 
Save Time, Stress and Money
 
There are many options available today for buying, installing and replacing doors and windows, so much so that choosing the right type, brand and style for your needs can become a stressful and time consuming experience. But it doesn’t have to be that way. Whether you need to install new windows in your custom home, replace existing windows or doors in your current residence, or are interested in saving money with new energy efficient models, we promise to deliver unmatched service and top-quality products at a competitive price. Some of the products and services we offer include:
 
Windows– We install vinyl windows in a variety of colours and styles, including casements, double hung and slider.
 
Doors– Choose from entrance doors available in insulated steel or fibreglass and in your choice of colour and gloss, as well as patio and garden doors in a selection of glass styles.
 
Railings– We are experienced in the installation of quality aluminum railings, available in various styles and colours.
 
Repairs– We offer repairs of most brands of doors and windows, as well as repairs for screens and glass performed in our shop.

Window Wise Certified

profile:
Vista One Retractable Screens supplies and installs the most innovative retractable screens for doors and windows. We have several models to choose from, those that Rollaway, and others that Foldaway. They all retract into a compact cassette when not in use. Our screens provide the best protection against flying insects while providing ventilation to your home.

There are four main components to Retractable Screens, whether they Rollaway or Foldaway - Housing, Mesh, Pull Rail/Slide Bar, Guide rails. 

Traditional fixed screens have limitations: they are unattractive, obstruct the view within and without; prone to damage; difficult to maneuver; hard to clean.

A retractable screen from Vista One is durable, safe and easy to operate. With our extensive line of screens to choose from we have a screen to compliment any home design. Our custom screens provide a seamless transition between indoor and outdoor living spaces, blending the best of both worlds!

Landmark Home Solutions have been supplying comfort and peace of mind to homeowners across Ontario since 1987. We’re proud to offer one of the most energy efficient windows available on the market today that offers homeowners a significant return on investment all while being backed with the strongest warranty in the business today!
 
We’re part of the Canadian Standards Association (CSA) and the Better Business Bureau, and in all the years we’ve been in business, we’ve never had an unresolved complaint. We’re members of SAWDAC (Siding and Window Dealers Association of Canada) and make sure that we meet their membership criteria, code of ethics and sign an ironclad five-year workmanship guarantee statement.
 
We’re also proud to say that our windows are Energy Star certified.  As you probably know, the international Energy Star symbol is a simple way for consumers to identify products that are among the most energy-efficient on the market. We also offer financing through TD Canada Trust, ensuring that our customers have a trustworthy partner too.
Based in St. Catharines, Ontario, 

Landmark Home Solutions is proud to represent our Canadian heritage in all that we do.  Our windows are made right here, so you know you’re getting the best quality windows in the world.

profile:
Q) Why are vinyl windows the best choice?
A) Your choice of framing material goes a long way toward determining the longevity and energy of the total window system. Wood windows possess excellent thermal qualities but are prone to weather deterioration and require painting at regular intervals. Aluminum windows are very durable but offer little insulating value because they conduct energy rapidly. Vinyl windows are your best choice because they offer thermal characteristics similar to wood are extremely durable and provide a finish that is virtually maintenance -free. Also keep in mind that the best performing vinyl window systems have multi-chambered frames with welded corners.

Q) What is argon gas and why is it used with Low E glass?
A) Argon is a safe odorless, colorless, non-toxic, non-flammable insert that is commonly used in place of air between the glass panes of an insulated Low E glass unit. Argon's heat conductivity is lower than that of air. And thus it is better insulator and contributes to a lower U-factor. Argon is not an effective solar performer by itself: that is why it is only used on conjunction with Low E insulated glass.

Q) What is an ENERGY STAR windows?

A) ENERGY STAR is a government-backed program helping businesses and individuals protect the environment through superior energy efficiency. ENERGY STAR-qualified vinyl windows and doors save you energy and money, increase the comfort of your home, and protect your valuable possessions from sun damage. They are also better for the environment because lowering your energy use means less air pollution from power plants. Save money and energy. Installing ENERGY STAR-qualified windows from GTA Windows and Doors lowers energy bills and saves you money over new double-paned, clear glass vinyl windows and vinyl patio doors.
Q) What is an Super Spacer and why is it important?
A) The Super Spacer is the best performing solution on the market. Super Spacer has a conductivity rate 25 times lower than aluminum spacers. Super Spacer not only eliminates your condensation problems, but also reduces the risk of thermal breakage. When you are planning to construct or renovate, demand the Super Spacer for your windows and doors and eliminate the battle of condensation and frost. Assure your self-comfortable viewing throughout the seasons.

Q) What is the U-factor?
A) The U-factor or U-value is the measure of a window's thermal efficiency, based on its resistance to the follow of energy. The lower the U-factor, the more thermally efficient the window. Most new window technology had been aimed at lowering U-factors through the use of three important innovations: INEX spacer, low emissivity glass coatings and argon gas.

Q) What is Low Emissivity glass?
A) Low Emissivity glass, commonly referred to, as Low E. is glass that has been coated with a micro-thin metallic film to improve thermal performance. The coating reduces the transfer of heat rays through the glass while still allowing light to pass through. In essence, the coating reflects heat back toward its source. Thus, heat from the furnace stays inside the home during cold weather, resulting in greater comfort and lower energy costs. Low E coatings also reduce harmful ultraviolet rays that cause drapes and upholstery to fade.

Q) Why should I choose GTA Windows Ind.?
A) GTA strives to offer window and door products that are both aesthetically appealing and energy-efficient. We closely monitor the quality of our products and back them with some of the best warranties in the business. In short we care about our customers and value their trust. We thank you for visiting our web site and would like you to consider GTA Windows and doors for your next remodeling project.

Q) What is the best way to get an estimate for new windows and doors?

A) You need to have someone come to your home, measure your openings, show you our samples before presenting you with an accurate, no obligation free estimate.
Q) What windows you company do and what area do you serve?

A) Specializing in energy star rated vinyl windows - energy efficient windows: casement windows, awning windows, double hung windows, single hung windows, bay windows, bow windows, vinyl single slider windows, double slider windows, picture windows and custom shape windows with windows and doors services in the Greater Toronto area, Ontario - Mississauga, Brampton, Oakville, Ajax, Pickering, Markham, Unionville, Thornhill, Woodbridge, Richmond Hill, Aurora and Toronto.

Metalex Security Products has much more to offer than just its many years in operation. The President and founder, Tom Reimer established the business in 1986 after a personal experience of having to break into his own home after losing his keys. The point of entry was through the basement window which provided easy access. It became immediately obvious that the basement windows were very vulnerable to break and enter. Tom devised a metal window guard for his windows and, subsequently, half the neighbourhood! Hence, Metalex Security Products was born.
 
We offer a multitude of services including retractable screens! Feel free to inquire more for details!

*Window Guards
*Juliette Balcony Railings
*Better Safe: Laser cut, anti pry door, Electronic key pad with programmable 4 button code, Emergency key override, Two removable shelves, Colour: Recreation white
*In Wall Security Steel Safe
*Various Door Styles and Colours
*Lock Options
*Grilles
*Decorative Ornamental Security Storm/ Screen Doors

Commercial Security Products:
*Folding Security Gates

*Barrier Gates
*Retractable Gates
*Security Curtains
*Fixed Gates (Man Door Gates)

profile:
Phantom Screens/ Ontario Screen Systems offers a beautiful alternative to traditional insect screens. Manufactured in Canada, Phantom retractable screens disappear when not in use and come in a variety of colours to match virtually any décor, all while blending in perfectly with door trim to maintaining the home’s architectural integrity. 

These screens can be cover all window types including casement, awning, single & double-hung, sliding and tilt ‘n’turn windows.

They are also customized for double french doors, swing in swing out doors, sliding doors, and oversized doors.

Motorized retractable screens by Phantom provide insect protection, climate control and solar shading without blocking your views.

Visit https://phantomscreens.ca/ and talk to a Screen Expert today.
products: All of Phantom Screens, including retractable screen doors, windows and motorized screens
services: Our trained installation technicians and the Limited Lifetime Warranty ensure that Phantom Screens last a lifetime.
specialities:
Once you've made contact with us at Ontario Screen Systems Inc., we will talk to you about your requirements and ideas you have. We’ll then take detailed measurements and prepare you an estimate. We'll also schedule an installation date with you.

Depending on how many doors and window screens you order, most installations are completed within one day. However, before we schedule an installation with you we will take into account any manufacturing lead times when ordering your screens. There are a number of installation options for our large opening (manual and motorized) screens including fully recessed and surface mounted and so the time taken for installation will vary for every project.

Our door and window screens, as well as our screens for large openings are professionally installed by Phantom-trained installers who will treat your home with care.

Call us today and experience Phantom Screens.

profile:
Notice: During the COVID-19 pandemic, Window Experts is operational during this time for all your needs. We are able to provide quotations and estimates through the practice of social distancing and safety measures. Call us today for a free quote at 416-844-0099!
  
 
The Window Experts is a Canadian company that has been installing Canadian-made, high-quality windows and doors, for over 15 years. We are committed to providing exceptional service to help transform your dream home into a reality, starting with your windows and doors.

The majority of our business is based on referrals from our satisfied customers, therefore, we work with integrity and want to be your number one choice for doors’ and windows’ replacements!

Our Services:
1) Installation services for builders and contractors:
We supply and install windows and doors from Window Wise certified manufacturers.

2) Installation services for windows and doors companies and manufacturers:
Windows and doors companies and manufacturers face several points of pressure. You need to cater to the volume of requests received as well as meet deadlines that might often be unreasonable.
In such situations, a reliable contractor, who can take the responsibility of professional installations off your hand, can be a blessing. At Window Experts, we realize that and we will be happy to assist you with any and all types of window-installations, including:

Brick to Brick installation (Vinyl Windows/Aluminum Windows)
Retrofit/Frame to Frame installation (Vinyl Windows)
Bay to build/Bow to build (with roof/with skirt)
Sliding Doors (any type of standard/custom)
Entrance Doors (Steel/Vinyl/Wood/Fiberglass)
Garden Doors (Steel/Vinyl/Wood/Fiberglass)

3) Inspection services:
The need to conduct regular window inspections has been, increasingly, receiving the recognition it deserves. Be it commissioned by regulatory authorities, builders/ contractors, or requested by homeowners themselves, inspections offer a window of opportunity to identify issues before they occur. The issues, in turn, might result in a loss of finances, time or health.

Take, for instance, the case of humidity. Condensation and frost that collect on the surface of poor quality windows can permeate and create moisture, inside homes. This will, in turn, have ramifications on inhabitants’ lung health, in the long run.

This is why, inspecting windows before purchasing them or signing with a contractor, is strongly recommended. Windows Experts offer independent inspection services for companies and clients who had already replaced their windows or doors, but have questions or concerns.

profile:
Exterior Doors & Windows from Olympia Town Aluminum
Exterior door
Serving Scarborough and the Area Since 1981
Install new windows and doors with Olympia Town Aluminum. We sell, install and repair exterior doors and windows. You can find everything from patio and storm doors to vinyl windows and bungalow eavestroughs.

Located in Scarborough, we’ve been serving the area for 31 years now. Our reputation for cleanliness and quality workmanship provides us with many referrals and repeat business. We’re professional and treat every home like our own.

The Benefits of New Exterior Windows & Doors
If you find your heating and cooling bills are too high, the solution could be the installation of new exterior windows and doors. Your old windows or doors may have let heat escape in the winter and allowed cool air to filter out during the summer. This forces you to run your heating and cooling units longer and more often. Consider new windows and doors and save on your energy bill.

Make an appointment for your window or door installation today.

Heritage Home Design is a full-service windows and doors installation company that wants to make your new or existing home look beautiful from the ground up. profile:
SMART CHOICE – WINDOW AND DOOR SYSTEM INC. We are one of the leading suppliers and installers of windows and doors in Toronto, that are specially made to save energy. Our large inventory includes every conceivable window and door styles that you can imagine, from sliders and casements to European style tilt and turns and picture windows to elegant patio doors to well-secured entry doors, complemented by a range of colors and maintenance free interior options.
***
Our Windows and Doors are built to the highest industry specifications and all our window frames and sashes are fusion-welded in the factory, for that robust strength, with a lifetime factory processed seal for air and water leakage.
***

profile:
Since 1978, homeowners have relied on EuroSeal to provide the best windows for the right prices. Our commitment to quality has served us particularly well, as we have grown from a grass roots family-run business to a leader in the industry.

Looking forward, Euro-Seal will continue to couple innovation and quality with our first eco-friendly window line, GreenStar™. The design and application of the GreenStar™ window system has set a new standard in the window industry.

GreenStar™ window frames are designed outperform all other frames. The Colonial design can suit any internal or external finish of a house. Euro-Seal Windows Industry Ltd manufactures with the latest automated technology to ensure greater precision and consistency. EuroSeal manufactures its products to 1/8th of an inch to fit snug into any opening. We spared no resource in the design and quality of the window, and we ensure that the window always works as well as the day it was installed.

profile:
Yash Window Industry Ltd. have been installing energy efficient windows and doors for Ontario homeowners since many years. Our business evolved out of the need to provide homeowners with beautiful, durable and energy-efficient windows and doors – This is what our business is based on. We understand that choosing new windows and doors is an important decision and therefore we work with you to ensure you find the right options to meet your homes design, functional needs, and budget.

If you are ready to replace your home’s windows and doors, you have found the right company. We offer a superior product manufactured and installed to perfection at a great price. We understand the importance of superior style, exceptional good looks and extraordinary quality. We combine these qualities with top of the line security, incredible durability and superior energy efficiency to produce windows and doors that meet all your needs and beautify your home.

Most companies in the fenestration industry have a lifetime warranty. Very few provide the service described. Avoid labor costs. Enjoy prompt, polite and punctual service. Yash window Industry Ltd. are owned and operated by Canadians whom customers, dealers, and installers trust to provide service, and parts when required and according to priority. There is no need to shout for service, ask and we shall be happy to fix what is broken. We get more referrals from services than installations!
warranty_terms: Yes. Kindly ask for details. Depends on service provided.

profile: This window system is manufactured using RAU-FIPRO™, a high-tech material developed by REHAU based on the company’s vast experience with fiber composites for aircraft and Formula 1 race cars. The material is a hybrid fiberglass and vinyl that combines the benefits of both materials without their drawbacks. Like vinyl, it can be extruded in a multi-chambered design and fusion welded. Plus, it provides the high stability, torsional stiffness and static properties of fiberglass. It also has a low thermal expansion ratio.

profile:
Whether you are an architect, interior designer, tradesman, or home owner, we at Sixpenny make your woodwork dreams come to life.

Having a combined 15+ years in the trades, design and craft world, Sixpenny brings a wealth of historical knowledge of Toronto's architectural past and also where it is heading in the future. With that knowledge, we provide a crossover of products, including architectural millwork, doors, windows, and interior/exterior woodwork. All being bespoke solid wood.

We bring the craft back to the trade. Back to the “old days”, when the same person you took your design to, was the same person who built your product. We are a small company and we want to keep it that way.

We do not want to be designers at Sixpenny, we want to bring your designs to life! Through this we will work with you from day one to help realize your dream. We will keep you updated every step of the way to ensure a quality product, delivered on time. Sixpenny likes to practice the old adage of “doing it once and doing it right”.

We're also licensed by the City of Toronto, B23451, so you can be sure we're committed to satisfying our customers.

profile:
With over 25 years experience. Windtek provides custom-crafted windows and doors made to your specifications in our own factory.

We offer a complete service from taking the measurements, manufacturing and installing the new doors and windows, to removing the old ones.

Our solid vinyl windows and steel doors are suitable for retrofits, additions, and new construction. We also provide storm doors and porch enclosures. Our professional, certified team can do any design of your choice, including glass etchings, to add a unique touch to your home or business.

We are a family-owned business serving the Greater Toronto Area and Golden Horseshoe of Ontario for more than 25 years. We stand behind our products with a Lifetime Warranty.

Energy Efficient Vinyl Windows
Free Low-e2 & Argon Gas
Insulated Entry Doors (Sliding, Garden, French)
Lifetime Warranty
Factory direct prices

profile:
Home Zilla is a name you can trust for all your residential and commercial garage door, home appliance and windows and doors needs. With our vast experience and knowledge, we offer all clients a quick service and high-quality workmanship.

No problem is too big or too small. We will service any door or appliance, regardless of the make and model, and replace and repair all types of sash and catchment windows. And to better serve our customers in a fast and efficient manner, an estimate or an installation can be scheduled directly from our website.

This convenient feature was added with our customer in mind to allow a hassle-free scheduling process, especially during emergency situations. Our technicians have over 10 years of industry experience under their belt. They are committed to continually educating themselves on new products that become available.

This means that you will always speak to an expert technician who will give you the facts that you need to make informed decisions. Our technicians care about this industry that they work for and will always treat your problem as if it were their own.

We stand by our commitment to providing excellent work at an affordable price and will not compromise on the quality of that work for any reason. Contact us today to schedule your service call. 
Service Areas:
• Mississauga • Burlington • Oakville • Hamilton • Downtown Toronto • North York
• East York • Thornhill • Richmond Hill • Maple • Aurora • Newmarket • Markham
• Whitby • Brampton

profile:
Craft Door was established in 1991 and with an established reputation for commitment to innovative design, unsurpassed craftsmanship and excellent client service, Craft Door offers the very best in manufacturing for residential and commercial purposes. What makes us stand out from the rest is our reputation for quality, innovation and reliability. Experience in the building and design industry which we strongly feel is fundamental in building strong, sound working relationships with our clients who are mostly Homeowners, designers, architects and builders. We achieve this by offering products of exceptional quality with outstanding customer service and our satisfaction guarantee.

That’s why they keep coming back to us.

Whether the house or project is a contemporary, or a historic design, we can make a suitable entry. Options such as transoms and sidelights can be added, as well many different options to make your entry special anything is possible. Exterior doors can be ordered in a variety of different wood types and styles. Solid wood and engineering construction of the finest wood species such as Mahogany, Cherry, Walnut, Maple and Oak are used in the design and manufacturing techniques to translate the customer’s vision in to a reality and the result is a functional work of art.
